title: "Goop Di Goop" (w/ D'Arcy Carden)
itunes:title: "Goop Di Goop" (w/ D'Arcy Carden)
description:
WE ARE HAPPY because the immensely hilarious NY Sister & LA Queen D’Arcy Carden is back on LC! 

Coming off the first I Don’t Think So, Honey! Live in LA, Matt & Bowen & D’Arcy debrief on the raucous night and catch up since D’Arcy’s last appearance on the show. They discuss the differences between NY & LA (and the differences don’t stop at Las Culturistas!), the 3 most evil people in the world, D’Arcy’s role as the antagonist in “An Emmy For Megan”, Set Life on The Good Place & Barry, the world of moderating panels & conducting interviews, and SO MUCH MORE. 

Plus, a call from Matt’s parents!
